However, for predeploys, the address in op-bindings/predeploys/addresses.go is used for checking and the address in packages/contracts-bedrock/src/libraries/Predeploys.sol is used for deploying.
If the addresses in the two files are not synchronized, then this will result in incorrect addresses being used when deployment.

